                <h2  class="mag-b " id="job1251259">

            
            <a href='/job/skills-development-manager-ackermans' class='subjob-title'>Skills Development Manager </a>


            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/full-time">Full Time</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-education/bachelors">Bachelors</a> , <a href="/jobs-by-education/national-certificate">National Certificate</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info">5 years</span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Location</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-location/western-cape'>Western Cape</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">City</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-city/cape-town'>Cape Town</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Field</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-field/human-resources">Human Resources / HR</a>&nbsp</span>

</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<ul>
	<li>We&rsquo;re hiring! Ackermans is seeking a Skills Development Manager to lead the delivery of a critical function that ensures compliance, supports funding, and enables capability building across the business.</li>
	<li>You will drive the implementation of our Skills Development Strategy and ensure alignment with the National Skills Act, the B-BBEE Skills Development pillar, and the transition to QCTO-aligned occupational qualifications.</li>
	<li>Bring your Training &amp; Development expertise, strong knowledge of BBBEE and W&amp;R SETA programmes, and the ability to coordinate complex Skills Development initiatives across multiple stakeholders in an evolving regulatory environment.</li>
	<li>If you&rsquo;re detail-oriented, resilient, and skilled in relationship management, coaching and influencing, this is your opportunity to lead a team and make a meaningful impact in a highly regulated and dynamic environment.</li>
</ul>

<p>JOB RELATED KNOWLEDGE &amp; SKILLS REQUIRED</p>

<p>KNOWLEDGE:</p>

<p>Essential:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Knowledge of BBBEE priority element: Skills development</li>
	<li>Working knowledge of W&amp;R SETA and its programmes</li>
	<li>Knowledge of the South African Qualifications Framework and classification of qualifications and institutions</li>
	<li>Understanding of the QCTO landscape and occupational qualification framework, including associated compliance requirements, learner pathways, and stakeholder coordination</li>
</ul>

<p>SKILLS:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Accreditation of skills and leadership programmes</li>
	<li>Application of legislative requirements applicable to learning and development</li>
	<li>Coordination of Skills Development initiatives within a complex regulatory environment (including QCTO-aligned processes)</li>
	<li>Full spectrum of learning and development processes</li>
	<li>Planning, organizing, monitoring and control</li>
	<li>Relationship management and influencing</li>
	<li>Financial analysis</li>
	<li>Detail orientation</li>
</ul>

<p>EXPERIENCE REQUIRED:</p>

<p>Essential:</p>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p>5 Years T&amp;D related experience, including SDF and / or implementation of BBBEE requirements</p>
	</li>
</ul>

<p>Preferred:</p>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p>Retail experience</p>
	</li>
</ul>

<p>QUALIFICATIONS REQUIRED</p>

<p>Essential:</p>

<ul>
	<li>3 years HR / Training related degree/diploma</li>
	<li>Further qualification in ETDP field recommended</li>
</ul>
<p>

<a class="anko-a tc-bl" href="javascript:;" onClick="document.getElementById('application-method').scrollIntoView()">go to method of application »</a>

</p>


</div>

        <h2  class="mag-b " id="job1251260">

            
            <a href='/job/co-manager-blue-route-mall-ackermans' class='subjob-title'>Co - Manager - Blue Route Mall </a>


            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/full-time">Full Time</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-education/matric">Matric</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info">2 years</span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Location</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-location/western-cape'>Western Cape</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">City</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-city/cape-town'>Cape Town</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Field</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-field/sales-marketing">Sales and Business Development</a>&nbsp</span>

</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<p><strong>Job purpose</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>The purpose of the job is to optimize sales and exceed customer expectations through the implementation of the operations strategy and effective management of staff.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Minimum requirements</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>You will represent and be a custodian of the brand of our store</li>
	<li>Be energetic and a self-starter</li>
	<li>Two (2) years retail experience which includes at&nbsp;<strong>least one year in a supervisory and or management position.</strong></li>
	<li>Outstanding merchandise management , stock and cost control skills</li>
	<li>The capacity to maintain high store standards</li>
	<li>A proven ability to influence and lead a team</li>
	<li>You will have a keen development orientation in that you will be inspired to develop yourself and fellow team members</li>
	<li>Ability to communicate effectively in English (written and verbal) and competence in a second official language would be a definite advantage</li>
	<li>Grade 12 or equivalent</li>
	<li>Further qualifications related to retail/business will be an advantage</li>
	<li><strong>NB: The person must have a strong Administration Skill.</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>

<a class="anko-a tc-bl" href="javascript:;" onClick="document.getElementById('application-method').scrollIntoView()">go to method of application »</a>

</p>


</div>

        <h2  class="mag-b " id="job1251261">

            
            <a href='/job/graduate-programme-retail-space-planner-ackermans' class='subjob-title'>Graduate Programme: Retail Space Planner </a>


            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/full-time">Full Time</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-education/national-certificate">National Certificate</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info"></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Location</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-location/western-cape'>Western Cape</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">City</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href='/jobs-city/cape-town'>Cape Town</a></span></li>


<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Field</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-field/graduate-jobs">Graduate Jobs</a>&nbsp , <a href="/jobs-by-field/ux-design-architecture">UX, Design and Architecture</a>&nbsp</span>

</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<ul>
	<li>Are you an energetic, ambitious, and qualified graduate looking for a practical learning experience in retail?</li>
	<li>Applications are now open for our Cape Town-based&nbsp;Retail Space Planner Graduate&nbsp;opportunity!</li>
</ul>

<p>At Ackermans we provide our graduates with hands-on behind-the-scenes industry experience, to give them direction and purpose for the future. If your application is successful, you will have you the opportunity to:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Get paid experience based in CPT</li>
	<li>Kickstart your career in retail</li>
	<li>Work with industry experts</li>
	<li>Gain cross-functional exposure</li>
	<li>Work in a flexible environment</li>
	<li>Explore your interests</li>
	<li>Gain working knowledge of future career possibilities</li>
	<li>Develop your work ethic and corporate brand</li>
</ul>

<p>Gain valuable exposure to Retail Space Planning!</p>

<p>Depending on your qualification and area of interest, you&rsquo;ll have the opportunity to gain hands-on experience in:</p>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p>Operations: Retail Space Planning (CAD)</p>
	</li>
</ul>

<p>Qualifications:</p>

<ul>
	<li>A completed qualification - eg. Diploma in architecture, interior design or architectural draughting (Revit proficiency)</li>
	<li>No prior full time work experience in your field of study</li>
</ul>

<p>SUCCESSFUL ATTRIBUTES:</p>

<ul>
	<li>An assertive self-starter with the ability to work well within a team</li>
	<li>Good organizational and planning abilities</li>
	<li>Excellent communication skills</li>
	<li>Sound administrative skills</li>
	<li>Flexible and tenacious with the ability to thrive under pressure</li>
	<li>Good leaning orientation</li>
</ul>

<p>T&amp;C&rsquo;s</p>

<ul>
	<li>South African citizenship</li>
	<li>The candidate is based in Cape Town</li>
</ul>
<p>

<a class="anko-a tc-bl" href="javascript:;" onClick="document.getElementById('application-method').scrollIntoView()">go to method of application »</a>

</p>


</div>

        <h2  class="mag-b " id="job1251262">

            
            <a href='/job/supervisor-parow-belhar-mall-new-store-opening-ackermans' class='subjob-title'>Supervisor - Parow / Belhar Mall (New Store Opening) </a>


            </h2>  

        <ul class="job-key-info">

<li><span class="jkey-title">Job Type</span> <span class="jkey-info"><a href="/jobs-by-type/full-time">Full Time</a></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Qualification</span> <span class="jkey-info"></span></li>

<li><span class="jkey-title">Experience</span> <span class="jkey-info"></span></li>

