</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<p><strong>Knowledge Skills &amp; Experience</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>Excellent customer care and communication skills.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Accurate and efficient till operating skills with a good track record of overs and unders.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>High standard of work on sales floor in terms of standards.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Good record of attendance and punctuality.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Consistent application of Ackermans values, policies and procedures.</li>
</ul>

